&lt;li&gt;Guide and navigate a web-first organization, educating and collaborating with design and product partners to build novel and delightful experiences on top of the entire operating system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take an inclusive, equitable approach to hiring and coaching technical talent, guiding both highly independent senior engineers as well as junior engineers learning how to be productive in ambiguity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
