&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience as a product-minded engineering manager, with at least 3 years leading teams building software for enterprise or governments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical background with proven success building and shipping enterprise or government-grade products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience integrating and working with AI/ML models and understanding their capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in highly ambiguous environments, and operate with urgency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience recruiting, scaling, and retaining engineering talent in a high-growth environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent leadership and communication skills, with ability to work effectively across functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of rapidly building domain expertise and translating complex stakeholder requirements into technical strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Startup experience, particularly in scaling products from zero to one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering with sales, customer success, and professional services teams to drive product adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
